160
00:07:59.437 --> 00:08:01.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evet! Biz kalıyoruz, bebeğim! Başardık!

161
00:08:01.981 --> 00:08:05.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
