291
00:14:43.716 --> 00:14:44.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tutarlı ol.

292
00:14:45.593 --> 00:14:46.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tamam.

293
00:14:46.886 --> 00:14:50.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Şimdiden gırtlak gırtlağa geldiler.
