295
00:14:53.058 --> 00:14:55.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tracy, sen de onun ruh eşisin.

296
00:14:55.394 --> 00:14:57.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
