314
00:15:45.569 --> 00:15:48.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
yapısal temelini oluşturuyor.

315
00:15:48.280 --> 00:15:51.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
