316
00:15:51.659 --> 00:15:53.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Şu işe bakın!

317
00:15:53.827 --> 00:15:55.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bekle, anlamadığım bir şey var.

318
00:15:55.245 --> 00:15:59.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
