391
00:19:34.464 --> 00:19:37.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hadi bakalım, elinden geleni ardına koyma.

392
00:19:37.259 --> 00:19:39.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Bunu bir kere çözdük,
