395
00:19:50.480 --> 00:19:52.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hoş geldiniz!
Her şey harika!

396
00:19:55.861 --> 00:19:57.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Eleanor, içeri gelsene.

397
00:19:59.656 --> 00:20:02.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sen, Eleanor Shellstrop, öldün.

398
00:20:02.910 --> 00:20:04.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
